PREVIEWPLACE arises from the product of a team concerned about the trabajostopograficos; currently has great capabilities our available tools (such as: tablets, smartphone, phones, etc...) and so it is necessary to make use of them in the proper way. Seen from this perspective, a group of students went to work on the analysis of topographic calculations and in the development of this application.

PREVIEWPLACE is a mobile application that seeks to facilitate topographical works of Cabinet for the optimization of times, capturing, calculating and graphing themes: differential leveling, leveling of profile, surveying, horizontal curves, curves of level among others.
Discover the wall in innovation event .

The idea of this application, arises from the need in civil engineering students as a necessary tool for easy realization of topographic calculations and checks ; in addition to providing support to professionals in the construction area for survey work , where it is not possible to work with high-tech instruments (computer, total station, etc. ) or require a preview of place to describe . Its development has been carried out by a multidisciplinary group of students from the Technological Institute of Tehuacan , consisting of 2 students in Computer Systems Engineering and 3 students in Civil Engineering .

Here are some benefits of working with PreviewPlace : 
 -Support for surveying where it is not possible to work with high-tech instruments . 
 -Minimizes time spent topographic calculations. 
 -Make calculations accurately. 
 -Obtiene a preview of place to describe through dynamic graphics. 
 -Agents in detail the characteristic topographic calculations work selected by the user. 
 -Provides quality sight through its dynamic graphs. 
 -Cost accessible
